value.string: This bot can be tested as a standalone bot by following below instructions.
Initialize the Log FIle path in localization Block.
Open the required policy in Horison and click on recall.
Run the bot and after bot run completes check the logs.

Enable the below if code block If you want to test this bot as a standalone bot.
